  <entry>
    <title>Python实战：打造一个智能文档批量生成工具</title>
    <link href="/2026/02/21/2025-02-21-intelligent-document-generator/"/>
    <url>/2026/02/21/2025-02-21-intelligent-document-generator/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="前言"><a href="#前言" class="headerlink" title="前言"></a>前言</h2><p>在日常办公中，经常需要批量生成大量格式相似的文档。比如：</p><ul><li>批量生成员工合同</li><li>批量发送客户通知函</li><li>批量制作证书</li></ul><p>这些工作如果手动完成，既耗时又容易出错。于是我用 Python 开发了一个<strong>智能文档批量生成工具</strong>，支持 Word 和 Excel 模板的批量替换和生成。</p><h2 id="项目简介"><a href="#项目简介" class="headerlink" title="项目简介"></a>项目简介</h2><p>这是一个基于 Python ttkbootstrap 开发的桌面应用程序，具有以下特点：</p><p>✅ <strong>现代化 UI</strong> - 基于 ttkbootstrap 的美观界面</p><p>✅ <strong>多种数据输入方式</strong></p><ul><li>手动单条录入</li><li>批量导入 Excel&#x2F;CSV</li></ul><p>✅ <strong>丰富的功能</strong></p><ul><li>支持自定义替换规则</li><li>智能识别 Excel 表头自动生成规则</li><li>支持自定义文件命名规则</li><li>实时进度显示</li></ul><h2 id="技术栈"><a href="#技术栈" class="headerlink" title="技术栈"></a>技术栈</h2><ul><li><strong>GUI 框架</strong>: ttkbootstrap</li><li><strong>文档处理</strong>: python-docx, openpyxl</li><li><strong>数据处理</strong>: pandas</li><li><strong>多线程</strong>: threading（避免界面卡顿）</li></ul><h2 id="核心功能实现"><a href="#核心功能实现" class="headerlink" title="核心功能实现"></a>核心功能实现</h2><h3 id="1-模板替换逻辑"><a href="#1-模板替换逻辑" class="headerlink" title="1. 模板替换逻辑"></a>1. 模板替换逻辑</h3><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs python"><span class="hljs-comment"># Word 文档替换</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">process_docx</span>(<span class="hljs-params">self, tmpl, out, data</span>):<br>    doc = Document(tmpl)<br><br>    <span class="hljs-comment"># 段落替换</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> p <span class="hljs-keyword">in</span> doc.paragraphs:<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> rule <span class="hljs-keyword">in</span> <span class="hljs-variable language_">self</span>.replacements:<br>            key = rule[<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;key&#x27;</span>]<br>            val = <span class="hljs-variable language_">self</span>.get_value_for_key(key, data)<br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> key <span class="hljs-keyword">in</span> p.text <span class="hljs-keyword">and</span> val <span class="hljs-keyword">is</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">not</span> <span class="hljs-literal">None</span>:<br>                p.text = p.text.replace(key, <span class="hljs-built_in">str</span>(val))<br><br>    <span class="hljs-comment"># 表格替换</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> table <span class="hljs-keyword">in</span> doc.tables:<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> row <span class="hljs-keyword">in</span> table.rows:<br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> cell <span class="hljs-keyword">in</span> row.cells:<br>                <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> p <span class="hljs-keyword">in</span> cell.paragraphs:<br>                    <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> rule <span class="hljs-keyword">in</span> <span class="hljs-variable language_">self</span>.replacements:<br>                        key = rule[<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;key&#x27;</span>]<br>                        val = <span class="hljs-variable language_">self</span>.get_value_for_key(key, data)<br>                        <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> key <span class="hljs-keyword">in</span> p.text <span class="hljs-keyword">and</span> val <span class="hljs-keyword">is</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">not</span> <span class="hljs-literal">None</span>:<br>                            p.text = p.text.replace(key, <span class="hljs-built_in">str</span>(val))<br><br>    doc.save(out)<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="2-Excel-表格智能识别"><a href="#2-Excel-表格智能识别" class="headerlink" title="2. Excel 表格智能识别"></a>2. Excel 表格智能识别</h3><p>导入 Excel 时，程序会自动读取表头，并根据表头生成替换规则：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs python"><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">import_data_file</span>(<span class="hljs-params">self</span>):<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">not</span> <span class="hljs-variable language_">self</span>.replacements <span class="hljs-keyword">and</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">len</span>(cols) &gt; <span class="hljs-number">0</span>:<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> messagebox.askyesno(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;智能提示&quot;</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&quot;检测到规则列表为空，是否根据Excel表头自动生成替换规则？&quot;</span>):<br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> col <span class="hljs-keyword">in</span> cols:<br>                key_name = <span class="hljs-string">f&quot;&#123;&#123;<span class="hljs-subst">&#123;col&#125;</span>&#125;&#125;&quot;</span><br>                <span class="hljs-variable language_">self</span>.replacements.append(&#123;<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;key&#x27;</span>: key_name, <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;desc&#x27;</span>: col&#125;)<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="3-多线程处理"><a href="#3-多线程处理" class="headerlink" title="3. 多线程处理"></a>3. 多线程处理</h3><p>为了避免大批量生成时界面卡顿，使用了独立线程：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs python"><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">start_generation_thread</span>(<span class="hljs-params">self</span>):<br>    <span class="hljs-comment"># 锁定UI</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> tab_id <span class="hljs-keyword">in</span> <span class="hljs-variable language_">self</span>.notebook.tabs():<br>        <span class="hljs-variable language_">self</span>.notebook.tab(tab_id, state=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;disabled&quot;</span>)<br><br>    <span class="hljs-comment"># 启动线程</span><br>    t = threading.Thread(target=<span class="hljs-variable language_">self</span>.run_generation, args=(data_list,))<br>    t.daemon = <span class="hljs-literal">True</span><br>    t.start()<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="使用示例"><a href="#使用示例" class="headerlink" title="使用示例"></a>使用示例</h2><h3 id="场景：批量生成员工入职通知"><a href="#场景：批量生成员工入职通知" class="headerlink" title="场景：批量生成员工入职通知"></a>场景：批量生成员工入职通知</h3><ol><li><p><strong>准备模板</strong>（Word）</p><figure class="highlight dust"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs dust"><span class="language-xml">尊敬的 </span><span class="hljs-template-variable">&#123;姓名&#125;</span><span class="language-xml"> 先生/女士：</span><br><span class="language-xml"></span><br><span class="language-xml">欢迎加入 </span><span class="hljs-template-variable">&#123;公司名&#125;</span><span class="language-xml">！</span><br><span class="language-xml">您的职位是 </span><span class="hljs-template-variable">&#123;职位&#125;</span><span class="language-xml">，入职日期为 </span><span class="hljs-template-variable">&#123;入职日期&#125;</span><span class="language-xml">。</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p><strong>准备数据</strong>（Excel）</p><table><thead><tr><th>姓名</th><th>公司名</th><th>职位</th><th>入职日期</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>张三</td><td>XX科技</td><td>工程师</td><td>2025-03-01</td></tr><tr><td>李四</td><td>XX科技</td><td>设计师</td><td>2025-03-05</td></tr></tbody></table></li><li><p><strong>运行程序</strong></p><ul><li>选择 Word 模板</li><li>导入 Excel 数据</li><li>点击生成</li></ul></li><li><p><strong>结果</strong><br>自动生成 <code>入职通知_张三.docx</code> 和 <code>入职通知_李四.docx</code></p></li></ol><h2 id="代码亮点"><a href="#代码亮点" class="headerlink" title="代码亮点"></a>代码亮点</h2><h3 id="1-灵活的命名规则"><a href="#1-灵活的命名规则" class="headerlink" title="1. 灵活的命名规则"></a>1. 灵活的命名规则</h3><p>支持自定义文件名模板，使用变量：</p><ul><li><code>&#123;template_name&#125;</code> - 模板文件名</li><li><code>&#123;index&#125;</code> - 序号</li><li><code>&#123;姓名&#125;</code> - 数据中的字段值</li></ul><p>例如：<code>&#123;template_name&#125;_&#123;姓名&#125;_&#123;index&#125;</code> 会生成 <code>入职通知_张三_1.docx</code></p><h3 id="2-键值智能匹配"><a href="#2-键值智能匹配" class="headerlink" title="2. 键值智能匹配"></a>2. 键值智能匹配</h3><p>Excel 导入的数据列名可能没有花括号，程序会自动处理：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs python"><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">get_value_for_key</span>(<span class="hljs-params">self, key, data</span>):<br>    <span class="hljs-comment"># 直接匹配</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> key <span class="hljs-keyword">in</span> data:<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> data[key]<br><br>    <span class="hljs-comment"># 去除大括号匹配</span><br>    clean_key = key.strip(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;&#123;&#125;&quot;</span>)<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> clean_key <span class="hljs-keyword">in</span> data:<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> data[clean_key]<br><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-literal">None</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="3-用户体验优化"><a href="#3-用户体验优化" class="headerlink" title="3. 用户体验优化"></a>3. 用户体验优化</h3><ul><li>进度条实时显示处理进度</li><li>错误日志记录</li><li>生成完成后自动打开输出文件夹</li><li>双击编辑表格内容</li></ul><h2 id="项目截图"><a href="#项目截图" class="headerlink" title="项目截图"></a>项目截图</h2><p>界面采用 ttkbootstrap 主题，视觉效果现代清爽：</p><ul><li>清晰的选项卡布局</li><li>直观的配置流程</li><li>友好的错误提示</li></ul><h2 id="安装与运行"><a href="#安装与运行" class="headerlink" title="安装与运行"></a>安装与运行</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-comment"># 安装依赖</span><br>pip install -r requirements.txt<br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 运行程序</span><br>python main.py<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="总结"><a href="#总结" class="headerlink" title="总结"></a>总结</h2><p>这个工具将原本需要几小时的工作缩短到几分钟，大大提高了办公效率。如果你也经常需要批量生成文档，希望这个项目能给你带来帮助！</p><hr><p><strong>项目地址</strong>: <a href="https://github.com/Zengweisong/Template">https://github.com/Zengweisong/Template</a><br><strong>依赖库</strong>: pandas, python-docx, openpyxl, ttkbootstrap</p>]]></content>
    
    
